The defendant Domingo Apanecatl-Zacarias was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Domingo Apanecatl-Zacarias is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Domingo Apanecatl-Zacarias was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
